columnConfigurations.columnName: Order items with GR created late (%)
columnConfigurations.columnAlias: Order items with GR created late (%)

dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until order items delivered (days)",
    "Time until order items received (days)",
    "Order items not committed (%)",
    "Order items with overdelivery (%)",
    "Order items with GR created late (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Stock transport order items delivered") 
        	AS "Time until order items delivered (days)",
		AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Stock transport order items received") 
    		AS "Time until order items received (days)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Stock transport order items not committed") * 100 
        	AS "Order items not committed (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Stock transport order items with overdelivery") * 100 
        	AS "Order items with overdelivery (%)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Stock transport order items with goods receipt created later than planned") * 100 
        	AS "Order items with GR created late (%)"
    FROM THIS_PROCESS
    GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
